rse-and-the-midwife-2020|archive-date=January 20, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> The [[United Nations]] has declared 2020 as the '''International Year of Plant Health'''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fao.org/plant-health-2020/home/en/|title=International Year of Plant Health 2020|last=|first=|date=|website=Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110174810/http://www.fao.org/plant-health-2020/home/en/|archive-date=January 10, 2020|access-date=January 18, 2020}}</ref> 2020 has been designated as '''International Year of Sound''' by the [[International Commission for Acoustics]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sound2020.org/|title=2020 - International Year of Sound|publisher=[[International Commission for Acoustics]]|language=en|access-date=February 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217010545/http://sound2020.org/|archive-date=February 17, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nThe [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]] has led to severe global [[Socio-economic impact of the 2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|socioeconomic disruption]].<ref name=\"NYT-20200229\">{{cite news |work=[[The New York Times]] |title=Here Comes the Coronavirus Pandemic: Now, after many fire drills, the world may be facing a real fire |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/29/opinion/sunday/corona-virus-usa.html |date=February 29, 2020 |access-date=March 1, 2020 |department=Editorial |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229211512/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/29/opinion/sunday/corona-virus-usa.html |archive-date=February 29, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n<!-- {{Skip to top and bottom}}\n{{sts|January}} -->\n\n==Events==\n===January===\n* [[January 2]] \u2013 The [[government of New South Wales]], [[Australia]], declares a [[state of emergency]] whilst the [[government of Victoria]], Australia declares a state of disaster amid large [[2019\u201320 Australian bushfire season|bushfires]] that 