59.DTL|work=[[San Francisco Chronicle]]|accessdate = 2009-05-05}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 10, 2007\n| [[Cleveland]],<br>[[Ohio]],<br>United States\n| Asa H. Coon, 14\n| 1 dead\n| 4 injured\n| [[SuccessTech Academy shooting]]. 14-year-old student Asa Coon, reportedly upset about a school suspension, went on a shooting spree at [[SuccessTech Academy]], an [[alternative high school]] in [[Cleveland]], [[Ohio]], wounding two students and two teachers. He then fatally shot himself in a classroom.<ref name=\"NYTimes 2007-10-11\">{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Maag|author2=Ian Urbina  |title=Student, 14, Shoots 4 and Kills Himself in Cleveland School|date=2007-10-10|url =https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/11/us/11cleveland.html?_r=1&hp&oref=slogin|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate = 2009-02-25}}</ref><ref name=\"clevelandfourshot\">{{cite news|title = Four shot at school, gunman kills himself|newspaper= [[The Plain Dealer]]|date = October 11, 2007|url = http://www.cleveland.com/schoolshooting/plaindealer/index.ssf?/schoolshooting/more/four_shot.html|first = Michael|last = O' Malley|author2 = Gabriel Baird|accessdate = 2009-03-01|url-status = dead|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090413185847/http://www.cleveland.com/schoolshooting/plaindealer/index.ssf?%2Fschoolshooting%2Fmore%2Ffour_shot.html|archivedate = April 13, 2009}}</ref><ref name=\"washington1011\">{{cite news|first=Joe|last=Milicia|title=4 Hurt, Gunman Killed in Ohio School|date=2007-10-11|url =https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/10/10/AR2007101001486.html|work=[[The Washington Post]]|accessdate = 2009-03-07}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 11, 2007\n| [[Amsterdam]], Netherlands\n| H\u00fcseyin P., 14\n| 1 dead\n|\n| A 14-year-old student, identified only as H\u00fcseyin P., stabbed 16-year-old classmate Youssef Mokhtari to death at a school in the [[Slotervaart (former borough)|Slotervaart]] borough of [[Amsterdam]]. The victim had reportedly made a joke about the surname of the perpetrator.<