5, arrested in stabbing incident|publisher=[[Vallejo Times Herald|Times-Herald]]|date=December 13, 2013|accessdate=December 31, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101000116/http://www.timesheraldonline.com/news/ci_24716086/vallejo-girl-15-arrested-stabbing-incident|archive-date=January 1, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Dts|December 16, 2013}}\n| [[Bradenton, Florida]], United States\n| \n|\n|  2 injured\n| A student stabbed two students with scissors at Lee Middle School. He was charged with aggravated battery.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bradenton.com/2013/12/17/4892902/lee-middle-school-student-charged.html|title=Lee Middle School student charged with stabbing two classmates|newspaper=[[Bradenton Herald]]|date=December 16, 2013|accessdate=December 31, 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101045400/http://www.bradenton.com/2013/12/17/4892902/lee-middle-school-student-charged.html|archivedate=January 1, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Dts|December 19, 2013}}\n| [[Fresno, California]], United States\n| Four suspects\n| \n| 1 injured\n| Four teens went into [[Edison High School (Fresno, California)|Edison High School]] in what was believed as a gang-initiation process. After accosting a 62-year-old woman about a mile away from school grounds, they found an athletic trainer who taught at Edison High and shot him several times in the leg and stomach. It took a few days for the youths to get caught, and this was cinched when the 62-year-old woman and some surveillance video gave police the information they needed.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kmph.com/story/24300106/fresno-police-arrest-four-teens-related-to-edison-high-school-shooting|title=Fresno Police Arrest Four Teens Related To Edison High School Shooting|publisher=KMPH Fox 26 News|author=Abovian, Ellina|date=December 25, 2013|accessdate=December 26, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abclocal.go.com/kfsn/story?section=news/local&id=9370006|title=Multiple arrests made