ayed-with-classmate_2387201.html|title=13-Year-Old Boy Impaled by Sword as He \u2018Played\u2019 With Classmate|newspaper=Epoch Times}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 19, 2018}}\n|[[Ulan-Ude]], Russia\n| Student, 15\n|\n| 6 injured\n| Five seventh-graders and their teacher were wounded when a ninth-grader in Buryatia's capital Ulan-Ude, near Lake Baikal in Siberia, attacked them with an axe and burned the classroom with a Molotov cocktail. One student was in critical condition. The attacker was detained and hospitalised after he tried to commit suicide.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/01/19/teen-russia-axes-students-burns-classroom-third-school-attack/ |title=Teen in Russia axes students and burns classroom in third school attack  in a week |publisher=telegraph.co.uk}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 22, 2018}}\n|[[Italy, Texas]] \n| \n|\n| 1 injured\n|A 16-year-old male student fired at a 15-year-old classmate in the cafeteria of [[Italy High School]]. The gunman left the school immediately after opening fire.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/01/22/shooting-at-texas-high-school-suspect-in-custody-police-say.html|title=Texas high school shooting leaves 1 student wounded; suspect in custody, police say|first=Katherine|last=Lam|date=22 January 2018|website=foxnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/texas-teen-charged-assault-italy-high-school-shooting-n840301|title=16-year-old boy charged in Texas shooting, wounded student remains hospitalized|website=nbcnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kwtx.com/content/news/Gunman-in-custody-Monday-at-Italy-High-School-some-injured-470519863.html|title=Paramedic: Girl wounded in area school shooting bravest \u2018I\u2019ve ever seen\u2019|first=John|last=Carroll|website=kwtx.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 22, 2018}}\n|[[New Orleans, Louisiana]] \n| \n|\n| 1 injured\n|Shots were fired from a truck in the parking lot of NET Charter High School, targeting a c